# Bike Sales Analysis

## 📌 Project Overview

This Excel dashboard analyzes bike sales data to identify customer purchasing behavior and sales performance.

## 🎯 Objectives

- Analyze bike sales
- Understand customer demographics
- Identify purchasing trends
- Build an interactive dashboard

## 🛠️ Tools

- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Pivot Charts
- Slicers
- Conditional Formatting

## 📊 Dashboard KPIs

- Total Sales
- Average Income
- Customer Age Distribution
- Commute Distance
- Purchase Status
- Gender Analysis

## 📈 Insights

- Customers with higher income were more likely to purchase bikes.
- Middle-aged customers represented the largest customer segment.
- Commute distance influenced purchasing decisions.

